---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Tirsasaki">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-blue-900 text-transparent bg-clip-text">
        Hello, I'm Tirsasaki
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Linux Writer
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-900 dark:text-green-100">About Me</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I'm a dedicated writer and developer focusing on Linux systems, particularly Arch Linux. 
          As an active contributor to Constellation Linux, I work on developing and improving Linux-based solutions.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through my website <a href="https://conslinux.com" class="text-green-800 hover:text-green-700 underline">conslinux.com</a>, 
          I share in-depth knowledge about Linux systems, focusing on Arch Linux tutorials, tips, and best practices.
          My goal is to make Linux more accessible and understandable for everyone.
        </p>
        <p>
          As a contributor to Constellation Linux, I focus on developing and documenting Arch Linux-based solutions. 
          My work involves creating comprehensive guides, troubleshooting documentation, and sharing best practices 
          for Linux system administration.
        </p>
        <p>
          Visit <a href="https://conslinux.com" class="text-green-800 hover:text-green-700 underline">conslinux.com</a> 
          to explore my latest articles, tutorials, and contributions to the Linux community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="https://github.com/tirsasaki" 
         class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-green-900 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-green-800 transition-colors">
